      "span_text": "We found an average pregnancy rate of 41% only with RSS. Similar data were reported by Pontes, et al.  , who obtained a 39% pregnancy rate in a large-scale program with over 5000 OPU-IVEP procedures in Bos taurus and Bos indicus-taurus cattle using sexed sperm (sex-sorted, freezethawed).",
